{"id": "1412347018940256307", "channel_id": "1412347018940256307", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "《艺术娱报》，只报猛料：\n本期，我们跟踪采访的是“刻画真实世界的写实主义者”皮克曼。\n\n✦他是天才，是异类，是被社会所排斥的癌细胞般的极端存在；\n✦谩骂也好，夸赞也罢，最终都会变成他画布上的艳丽色彩。\n✦据说他的画拥有模糊真实与虚假的神奇魔力，进入画中的人将看见世界的真相！\n\n订阅《艺术娱报》，小编将陆续为大家揭晓皮克曼与其画中的秘密，下面是第一期报道：\n\n——✦——✦—— ✦✦✦ ——✦——✦——\n\nArt & Scandal Gazette，we only break the big ones.\nIn this issue, we track an interview with Pickman, the \"realist who depicts the true world.\"\n\n✦He is a genius, an outlier, an extreme existence like a cancer cell rejected by society;\n✦Whether it's insults or praise, in the end, they will all become the vibrant colors on his canvas.\n✦It is said that his paintings possess a magical power that blurs the line between reality and illusion; those who enter the painting will see the Hidden Truth of the world!\n\nSubscribe to \"Art & Scandal Gazette\", and our editor will gradually reveal the secrets of Pickman and his paintings. Here is the first issue report:", "timestamp": "2025-09-02T08:02:49.454000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-09-02T08:05:28.749000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "❤️", "emoji_id": null, "count": 27}, {"emoji": "cute1", "emoji_id": "1356053053568192717", "count": 4}, {"emoji": "wow", "emoji_id": "1356053147029864518", "count": 2}], "attachments": [{"id": "1412347021985185902", "filename": "--1-.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 21415151, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1412347018940256307/1412347021985185902/--1-.jpg?ex=6a003baa&is=69feea2a&hm=4a596960a389f647f12ec23bad2e07546ac684560d0f5f8eefaeb38a901d7269&"}, {"id": "1412347024912683018", "filename": "--1-.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 23503646, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1412347018940256307/1412347024912683018/--1-.jpg?ex=6a003baa&is=69feea2a&hm=5ed491dc687dcc222ce2705b21b94157ac119e2cc1c65301deb32beb1860d49e&"